(ns ui.components.dashboard
  (:require [reagent.core :as r]
            [re-frame.core :as rf]
            [reitit.frontend.easy :as rfe]
            [ui.subs :as subs]
            [ui.events :as events]
            [ui.components.charts :as charts]))

(defn format-currency [amount]
  (when amount
    (.toLocaleString amount "en-US" #js {:style "currency" :currency "USD"})))

(defn account-summary-card []
  (let [account-summary @(rf/subscribe [::subs/account-summary])
        total-nav @(rf/subscribe [::subs/total-nav])]
    [:div.card.mb-4
     [:div.card-header.d-flex.justify-content-between.align-items-center
      [:h5.mb-0 "Account Summary"]
      [:button.btn.btn-sm.btn-outline-primary.refresh-btn
       {:on-click #(rf/dispatch [::events/fetch-account-summary])}
       [:i.bi.bi-arrow-clockwise] " Refresh"]]
     [:div.card-body
      (if account-summary
        [:div.row
         [:div.col-md-3
          [:div.metrics-tile
           [:h6 "Total NAV"]
           [:h3 (format-currency total-nav)]]]
         [:div.col-md-3
          [:div.metrics-tile
           [:h6 "Daily P&L"]
           (let [daily-pl (:daily-pl account-summary)]
             [:h3 {:class (if (pos? daily-pl) "positive-value" "negative-value")}
              (format-currency daily-pl)])]]
         [:div.col-md-3
          [:div.metrics-tile
           [:h6 "Open Positions"]
           [:h3 (or (:open-position-count account-summary) "0")]]]
         [:div.col-md-3
          [:div.metrics-tile
           [:h6 "Margin Used %"]
           [:h3 (str (or (:margin-used-percent account-summary) "0") "%")]]]]
        [:p "Loading account summary..."])]]))

(defn performance-chart-card []
  (let [performance-data @(rf/subscribe [::subs/performance-data])]
    [:div.card.mb-4
     [:div.card-header.d-flex.justify-content-between.align-items-center
      [:h5.mb-0 "Performance Chart"]
      [:button.btn.btn-sm.btn-outline-primary.refresh-btn
       {:on-click #(rf/dispatch [::events/fetch-performance-data])}
       [:i.bi.bi-arrow-clockwise] " Refresh"]]
     [:div.card-body
      (if performance-data
        [charts/performance-chart performance-data]
        [:p "Loading performance data..."])]]))

(defn recent-positions-card []
  (let [positions @(rf/subscribe [::subs/positions])
        top-positions (take 5 positions)]
    [:div.card.mb-4
     [:div.card-header.d-flex.justify-content-between.align-items-center
      [:h5.mb-0 "Recent Positions"]
      [:a.btn.btn-sm.btn-outline-primary {:href (rfe/href :positions)} "View All"]]
     [:div.card-body
      (if positions
        [:table.table.table-hover
         [:thead
          [:tr
           [:th "Instrument"]
           [:th "Type"]
           [:th "Units"]
           [:th "Value"]
           [:th "P&L"]]]
         [:tbody
          (for [position top-positions]
            ^{:key (:instrument position)}
            [:tr
             [:td [:a {:href (rfe/href :instrument-detail {:id (:instrument position)})}
                   (:instrument position)]]
             [:td (:type position)]
             [:td (:units position)]
             [:td (format-currency (:current-value position))]
             [:td {:class (if (pos? (:pl position)) "positive-value" "negative-value")}
              (format-currency (:pl position))]])]]
        [:p "Loading positions..."])]]))

(defn dashboard-view []
  [:div
   [:h1.my-4 "Trading Dashboard"]
   [account-summary-card]
   [performance-chart-card]
   [recent-positions-card]])
